rows.label: tlk502103_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, you're new around here, right?

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0002
rows.name: Yeah. What about it?

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0003
rows.name:
Have you been a mercenary for a
while.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0004
rows.name: A fair while, I guess.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0005
rows.name:
I bet you've got a ton of cool stories
about life as fighter-for-hire!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0011
rows.name: Hmmm... Lemme think...

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0012
rows.name:
Tell me about...the job that you earned
the most money on!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0013
rows.name: Ah...Well, that's easy...

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0014
rows.name:
You know the mine
near Fons Maim?

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0015
rows.name: Yeah, I know it.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0016
rows.name:
Back in the day, they used to mine
some real valuable stuff out of there...

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0017
rows.name: Really? Wow!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0018
rows.name:
But one time a bunch of monsters
made a nest down there. So we got
asked to go and clear 'em out!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0019
rows.name:
The folks who were mining out of
there were making top-dollar. So the
pay packet was pretty nice!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0020
rows.name:
Yeah, they're a pretty influential bunch,
I guess.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0021
rows.name:
We took care of 'em and cleaned the
place up, but in no time at all, the little
bastards set up shop there again!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0022
rows.name:
It's like they didn't know when to
quit. We'd bash 'em up, and then
they'd be back for more.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0023
rows.name:
Didn't matter to us. Every time we
cut 'em down to size - Kerching!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0024
rows.name: Cool!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0025
rows.name:
And we got paid like twenty times,
thanks to those monsters!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0026
rows.name:
On the 21st time... Well, the quarry
fell in, 'cos of all the fighting.
That's how bad-ass we are!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0027
rows.name: You've really got a colorful history...

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0028
rows.name:
Ah, I got all giddy talking about it
there!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0029
rows.name:
No worries! It's really awesome to
think about it!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0030
rows.name:
Hey, did you ever take any of the ore
from that mine, back in the day?

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0031
rows.name: Yeah, I still have some. You want it?

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0032
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Huh?
Yeah!

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0041
rows.name: Sorry, I don't feel like talking about it.

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0042
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Huh?
That's odd...

rows.label: tlk502103_msg0043
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Perhaps my charm failed me this time.
